        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 3. Dicranophragma (B.) relictum Mederos sp. nov. A. Wing venation. B–H. Variations detected in some specimens such as extra cross veins (C, F–H) and the split at the end of M 3 vein creating a cell (D), as well as variations in the length and shape of cell dm and cell m1 (B, F–H). Scale bar = 1.0 mm." ;
